MTN has announced new deals for new and existing customers who get a new contract today or change their service price plan. JOHANNESBURG MTN has offered 50GB of free data and 10,000 minutes per month to new and existing customers.The new deal is only available on 13 January and is available to customers who sign up for a new contract or perform an upgrade to certain price plans.The free 50GB of data and 10,000 MTN-to-MTN minutes per month will be provided to subscribers for the duration of their 24-month contract.